longBusinessSummary: Divio Technologies AB (publ) operates as a PaaS and cloud management software company. The company provides cloud management and managed cloud hosting, cloud infrastructure, cloudflare, application security, backups, cloudShift, and mirrors. It serves Switzerland, the Nordic countries, the United States, England, Holland, and Germany. The company was incorporated in 2016 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden.
